data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Price Improvement!   What a LAKE VIEW! Set your sights on this coveted VILLA in the GATED village of DOVES LANDING in WEST MEADOWS, Tampa Palms! LAKEFRONT end unit home sits in a cul-de-sac on a large open pie shape lot offering great privacy with tranquil views of the pond that goes into a  20-acre lake and preserve.  Large & Spacious 3 bedroom/ 2 bath 2- Car Garage Villa Ready for new owners to put their personal touches in.  In the oversized primary bedroom with a tray ceiling has plenty of space for a sitting area or office and has sliding glass doors to the screened lanai where you will see beautiful sunsets over the pond. You will enjoy the large walk-in closet and second closet, ensuite bath with dual sinks, soaking tub, separate shower, and private water closet. The secondary bedrooms are split from the primary bedroom offering privacy for guests.  Doves Landing residents have their own private community pool plus full access to West Meadows amenities including the community pool, fitness center, tennis courts, playground, and basketball courts. Maintenance includes exterior painting, roof, lawn service, community pool and gated entrance. Pretty much MAINTENANCE FREE. HVAC is approx 2018/2019. Doves Landing is located just minutes to I-75, Moffitt Cancer Center and University of South Florida.So much to love about this community!
